    <note type="biography">
        <p>Brewer, landowner, and agriculturist. Major in the volunteers. Partner in the brewing firm Hallett &amp; Abbey, Hove, Sussex. Farmed at Black Rock, Brighton, Sussex. Developed pedigree strains of wheat, and established a seed company. Fellow of the Linnean Society, 1862.</p></note>
